title: Dynamo Bake
description: Small cozy bakery, with 5-6 tables, combined with a bike rental place. Serves cookies, cakes and baked goods for breakfast, afternoon tea time or take away. All food is made-in-house from scratch with lactose free and vegan choices. Serves raw desserts. Wi-fi with password. Options not labeled vegan, but owner speaks English and will happily explain which items are vegan. Catering and delivery are available.
